.TH SAMDISK "1" "February 2026" "SAMdisk 4.0 ALPHA (Feb  2 2026), (c) 2002-26 Simon Owen" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
SAMdisk \- command-line disk image utility
.SH DESCRIPTION
SAMdisk 4.0 ALPHA (Feb  2 2026), (c) 2002\-26 Simon Owen
.IP
SAMDISK [copy|scan|format|create|list|view|info|dir|rpm] <args>
.TP
\fB\-c\fR, \fB\-\-cyls\fR=\fI\,N\/\fR
cylinder count (N) or range (A\-B)
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-head\fR=\fI\,N\/\fR
single head select (0 or 1)
.TP
\fB\-s\fR, \fB\-\-sector[s]\fR
sector count for format, or single sector select
.TP
\fB\-r\fR, \fB\-\-retries\fR=\fI\,N\/\fR
retry count for bad sectors (default=5)
.TP
\fB\-R\fR, \fB\-\-rescans\fR=\fI\,N\/\fR
rescan count for full track reads (default=0)
.TP
\fB\-d\fR, \fB\-\-double\-step\fR
step floppy head twice between tracks
.TP
\fB\-f\fR, \fB\-\-force\fR
suppress confirmation prompts (careful!)
.SS "The following apply to regular disk formats only:"
.TP
\fB\-n\fR, \fB\-\-no\-format\fR
skip formatting stage when writing
.TP
\fB\-m\fR, \fB\-\-minimal\fR
read/write only used MGT tracks
.TP
\fB\-g\fR, \fB\-\-gap3\fR=\fI\,N\/\fR
override gap3 inter\-sector spacing (default=0; auto)
.TP
\fB\-i\fR, \fB\-\-interleave\fR=\fI\,N\/\fR
override sector interleave (default=1)
.TP
\fB\-k\fR, \fB\-\-skew\fR=\fI\,N\/\fR
override inter\-track skew (default=1)
.TP
\fB\-z\fR, \fB\-\-size\fR=\fI\,N\/\fR
override sector size code (default=2; 512 bytes)
.TP
\fB\-b\fR, \fB\-\-base\fR=\fI\,N\/\fR
override lowest sector number (default=1)
.TP
\fB\-0\fR, \fB\-\-head[0\fR|1]=N
override head 0 or 1 value
.PP
See https://simonowen.com/samdisk/ for further details.
.SS "Supported image types:"
.IP
R/W: DSK SAD DTI HFE MFI QDOS SAP ADF MBD OPD D88 1DD LIF D2M D4M D81 MGT CPM FD RAW
R/O: TD0 SCL FDI IPF MSA CQM CWTOOL UDI IMD SBT DFI SCP STREAM WOZ PDI A2R D80 ST BPB DMK 2D TRD CFI DSC SDF S24 DS2
.SS "Build features:"
.IP
zlib bzip2 lzma libusb1
